# Cloudflare Web Analytics — PUBLIC beacon token (safe to expose; embedded in client JS).
# Get it: Cloudflare dashboard -> Web Analytics -> Add site (gasalaza.com) -> copy token.
# Build-time var: Vite inlines it at build, so set it in the Railway build env and redeploy.
# Leave empty locally — the beacon only loads in production builds.
VITE_CF_BEACON_TOKEN=
